<subSubSection id="1B197EAD6B4D785C14DD03F438A370D1" pageId="25" pageNumber="112" type="type material">
<paragraph id="608716B15E75CDDBE2A86BC5EE3F3E13" pageId="25" pageNumber="112">Type material.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="85CADE6574C93D6319DE9F310147AF49" pageId="25" pageNumber="112">
Holotype: male (UASM) with following label data: &quot;BRASIL Amazonas / Rio Negro Cucui / varzea forest / Sept. 17, 1978 // BRASIL EXP. / 1978 / G.E.&amp; K.E. Ball / Collectors&quot;. Paratypes: 5 (2 male, 3 female) in UASM, ZSM from the type locality [1♂, UASM], &quot;Brasilien / Tapurucuara am / Rio Negro/Amazonas / 7 11.1963 / C. Lindemann&quot; [1♂, 1♀, ZSM], &quot;BRASIL Amazonas / Rio Demiti, ca. / 
<geoCoordinate id="E6621F04446598FCAF6B12C0BF8A6C0A" direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="925" value="0.8833333">0°53'N</geoCoordinate>
<geoCoordinate id="5181D0375102683F37CE4674E14CE7FC" direction="west" orientation="longitude" precision="925" value="-66.95">66°57'W</geoCoordinate>
/ &quot;La Laguna&quot; / Varzea forest / Sept. 13, 1978 // BRASIL EXP. / 1978 / G.E.&amp; K.E. Ball / Collectors&quot; [1♀, UASM], BRASIL Amazonas / ca. 10 km. n.e. / 
<normalizedToken id="164E9EA27CF49F42FA54705FEAEC4A51" originalValue="São">Sao</normalizedToken>
Gabriel da / Cachoeira, stream / margin, forest / Sept. 20, 1978 // BRASIL EXP. / 1978 / G.E.&amp; K.E. Ball / Collectors&quot; [1♀, UASM].
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C015BB7595E928998E3DE942E7450C94" pageId="25" pageNumber="112" type="type locality">
